Menu_SetHelpMessage
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Menu=>menu/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Menu_SetHelpMessage
Veneer:	<menu_set_help_message>
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = Menu object ID
r2 = 16
r3 = pointer to message text
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:		Method sets help text for the menu.